description:
Shakky explains why Sabaody Archipelago seems to be crawling with bounty hunters – eleven of the Grand Line`s most wanted pirates are currently ashore and two of them are in Luffy`s crew!
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Arata na Rival Shuuketsu! 11-nin no Choushinsei
Les nouveaux rivaux se rencontrent ! Les 11 Supernovae
تجمّع الأنداد الجدد! السّوبرنوفا الأحد عشر!
新たなライバル集結! 11人の超新星
